		<td><b>NES games with the best animation</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I'm curious to find some of the best examples of quality animation on the NES console. Two that come to mind for me are Metal Storm and Moon Crystal. Wondering if there's anything on the same level in terms of smoothness of animation and frame rate.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
