		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Maybe Prince of Persia or Aladdin? Aladdin was back ported from the SNES. Why restrict yourself to NES? People were sketching sprites on graph paper and entering them as hexadecimal numbers into text only consoles in those days. Of course their animations could be improved on. We have so much better tools to work with today.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
